name: XENON1T S2(x, y) correction map
description:
XENON1T S2 xy correction map
Version 0.3
Created 17th February 2017 by Adam Brown

Extracted from November 2016 Kr83m calibration (summed 41.6 keV peak)
Using 31 datasets totalling 1 days 01:47:24 between 2016-11-14 10:54:52 and 2016-11-15 14:42:13
Made using data processed with pax v6.2.0
